type: Tutorial Step - A Couple More Things!

definition.text: There's a couple more things I want to tell you about before I let you go! Bear with me!

paragraphs.text: I'll give you a quick introduction on what we are working on for upcoming versions of Superalgos! I mentioned Machine Learning algorithms, but there's more! It has to do with integrating crypto projects!

I also want to let you know that—if you appreciate what we are doing—you can help! Tens of thousands of hours of hard work have gone into building Superalgos and bringing it to its current state. I hope you can take a couple of minutes of your time to give back, and I'll be happy to tell you where to start!
